<section id="Section575202">
  <title>
      <anchor id="Anchor575201" role="Index" xreflabel="opportunities:stages for"/> 
      <indexterm significance="normal">
         <primary>opportunities</primary>

         <secondary>creating new stages for</secondary>
      </indexterm>Opportunity Stage</title>

  <para id="Para575238">To create a new Opportunity Stage, select the NEW
  button. The following screen will appear:</para>

  <para id="Para575242">
      <screenshot>
         <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
               <imagedata fileref="images/CRM_MI_optyStagesNew.png" id="Graphic575240"/>
            </imageobject>

            <caption id="Caption575243">Create New Opportunity Stage</caption>
         </mediaobject>
      </screenshot>
   </para>

  <para id="Para575244">When creating a new Opportunity Stage, you are
  presented with the following options:</para>

  <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
         <term id="Para575245">Name</term>

         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1848ab4">
            <para>Enter a name to define the Opportunity Stage.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
         <term id="Para575246">Description</term>

         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1848afc">
            <para>Enter a brief description of the Opportunity Stage.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>

  <para id="Para575247">To the far right of the screen, the following buttons
  are available:</para>

  <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
         <term id="Para575248">CANCEL</term>

         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1848b68">
            <para>Closes the screen without creating an Opportunity Stage,
        returning you to the previous screen.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
         <term id="Para575249">SAVE</term>

         <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1848bb0">
            <para>Creates the Opportunity Stage and adds it to the master list of
        Opportunity Stages.</para>
         </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>